{"tid":1643563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［黃懲罰］嬲！長沙灣小食店公然支持暴徒同犯民","createTime":"2019-10-10T07:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T19:25:42.000Z","uid":332624,"like":1119,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":185,"replies":[{"pid":"ae88dfd1d24a1e79bc74325ecdfe9a57c2876841","tid":1643563,"uid":332624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:41:48.000Z","msg":"琴日返屋企嗰陣諗住買啲嘢食，攞完野食準備走啦，突然有個邨入面好出名既<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯義工</span></span></strong>好惡咁走黎同老細講<span style=\"color: red;\">「你地做咩淨係黐呢條友既海報(民主派)，點解唔黐埋另一個(民建聯)」</span>，仲好兇咁話<span style=\"color: red;\">「邨入面個個都俾面我，你俾面就拆左個海報佢」</span>小弟嚇撚左一跳，原來民建聯既義工可以咁惡恐嚇商舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今朝翻學經過舖頭，間舖居然無拆到張海報，仲要貼住張捐錢俾星火既收據同香港人加油咁既反動海報，小弟真係好嬲啊佢地居然咁明目張膽支持呢班暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，要好好地懲罰呢間舖頭，要佢地做到唔停手啊啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">店舖名：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「包餃店」</span><br />\n地址：長沙灣幸福邨幸福商場地下G09號舖</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n貼咗當區民主派候選人既宣傳同香港人加油<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pBDi7th.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpBDi7th.jpg&h=5e92b7d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n捐錢俾星火<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9vQYAg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9vQYAg.jpg&h=2e1ae6a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0504aa506972b1f20a30b925c6780aecf509fd02","tid":1643563,"uid":268131,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"好型！"},{"pid":"714ec00fa0cf2c475890d9ca2bb219cc18d5a286","tid":1643563,"uid":332624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:44:46.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9312809e51f623803fa42675700857739b974ae9","tid":1643563,"uid":332624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:51:14.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"a81cc878f95b49b5664d8e1ad42bf3e59033abc6","tid":1643563,"uid":9564,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"要罰了"},{"pid":"d219b7cad6c60b8f1967215d6ad3ce9348a8a3b9","tid":1643563,"uid":233651,"like":148,"dislike":0,"score":148,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"又一間店唔想放工"},{"pid":"75f8d6b458c6f5cb3ccdcee3a0a7a4ed775999e2","tid":1643563,"uid":223525,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"真係未死過<br />\n等我好好用金錢懲罰你"},{"pid":"2a16a13eb6b105ca2dc11e64f125ce37d34c6b17","tid":1643563,"uid":109853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:55:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09421839c40b4733a67363d8bd1ca78f240e80f3","tid":1643563,"uid":286131,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用錢買嗮你d粉腸等你沒得開鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4538d4fae36389bd164b464e19045fda8eb5d177","tid":1643563,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\